개행문자 변경도 하지마세요.
하하하하하
즐건 코딩 되세요~~~~</textarea>

							</td>
						</tr>
					</table>
					<div class="bottom">
						<a href="/board">취소</a>
						<input type="submit" value="수정">
					</div>
				</form>				
			</div>
		</div>
		<%-include('../includes/navigation') %>
		<%-include('../includes/footer') %>
	</div>
</body>
</html>